<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//WAPFORUM//DTD XHTML Mobile 1.0//EN" "http://www.wapforum.org/DTD/xhtml-mobile10.dtd"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="zh-CN"><head><meta content="initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width" name="viewport"/><meta content="application/xhtml+xml; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/><meta content="no-cache" name="Cache-Control"/><title>搜索设置</title><style>h2,p{margin:0;padding:0}a{text-decoration:none;color:#1967d2}body{margin:16px;font-family:Arial;background:#fff}.Ls60h{font-size:18px;font-weight:400;max-width:550px;min-width:100px;margin:0 auto}.J0Gjlc{border-bottom:1px solid #dadce0}.ux2uR{border:unset}.JgLRQ{color:#202124;font-weight:400;font-size:22px;line-height:24px;padding:24px 0 16px}.J0Gjlc select{padding:4px 8px;background:#fff;color:#4d5156;border:1px solid #dadce0}.fRV4Nd{color:#4d5156;font-size:14px}.ttsJHf{padding:16px 0}.zhqPEd{font-size:14px;color:#4d5156;padding-bottom:16px}.ttsJHf a{color:#fff font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400}.w95eXc{color:#202124;font-size:11px;padding-top:4px}.C2AuFf{padding:36px 0}.V0BPAb{padding:16px 0;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;color:#4d5156}.V0BPAb a{color:#4d5156}.tFbySd{width:113px;height:32px;margin-right:8px;border:1px solid #dadce0}.UYoHv{color:#fff;background-color:#1a73e8}.sAqXmb{color:#4d5156;background-color:#fff}.JWjuld{padding-bottom:16px;display:inline-block}.ci0Ncb{padding:0 8px}</style></head><body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:small"><style>.ZZpONc{font-size:15px;color:#4d5156}</style><img style="margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle" src="https://www.gstatic.com/images/branding/searchlogo/1x/google_logo_nonflagship_pref_page_color_58x19dp.gif" alt="Google" height="17" width="48"/><span class="ZZpONc">搜索设置</span><div class="Ls60h" style="width:550px"><form action="/setprefs" method="GET" name="langform"><input value="0__pwULChOjIrp_DxN-7whChhY3xo=" name="sig" type="hidden"/><div><style>.SmxyY{padding:16px;margin:16px;font-size:14px;background-color:#dadce0;display:block}</style><span class="SmxyY">您的 Cookie 似乎被停用了。您必须在浏览器中启用 Cookie，然后才能使用偏好设置。<a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/61416?hl=zh-CN">如何启用 Cookie？</a></span></div><div class="J0Gjlc"><h2 class="JgLRQ">活动</h2><p class="fRV4Nd">当"定制化搜索结果"设置处于开启状态时，Google 会根据此浏览器中的搜索记录为您提供更贴合需求的搜索结果和推荐内容</p><div class="ttsJHf"><div class="zhqPEd">搜索记录<span class="ci0Ncb">&gt;</span><a href="/url?url=https://myactivity.google.com/product/search/controls%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dpref-page%26hl%3Dzh-CN%26authuser%3D0&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;opi=89978449&amp;sa=U&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiyzM-W5tWDAxXSfvUHHfM5B1MQ7JsICAE&amp;usg=AOvVaw2cLoe1r271QwqkD9-Geslv">不保存</a></div></div></div><div class="J0Gjlc"><h2 class="JgLRQ">内容</h2><p class="fRV4Nd">通过对个性化和露骨内容进行偏好设置，管理系统显示的搜索结果类型</p><div class="ttsJHf"><div class="zhqPEd">个性化结果<span class="ci0Ncb">&gt;</span><a href="http://www.google.com/url?url=/setting/search/privateresults%3Fhl%3Dzh-CN%26authuser%3D0&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;opi=89978449&amp;sa=U&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiyzM-W5tWDAxXSfvUHHfM5B1MQ-vUJCAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3cqRNi6eXYnxzSC-u5TGHW">已关闭</a></div><div class="zhqPEd">安全搜索<span class="ci0Ncb">&gt;</span><a href="http://www.google.com/url?url=/safesearch%3Fhl%3Dzh-CN%26prev%3Dhttps://www.google.com/preferences%3Fhl%253Dzh-CN&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;opi=89978449&amp;sa=U&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiyzM-W5tWDAxXSfvUHHfM5B1MQ1fMKCAM&amp;usg=AOvVaw2_sUzOftQs2BFopGyXHG-a">“模糊处理”已开启</a></div></div></div><div class="J0Gjlc"><h2 class="JgLRQ">语言和区域</h2><p class="fRV4Nd">为按钮和其他显示文字选择偏好语言。<a href="https://support.google.com/websearch/?p=display_language&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=pref-page&amp;hl=zh-CN">了解详情</a></p><div class="ttsJHf"><div class="zhqPEd"><label for="K8H6ob">语言</label>&nbsp;<select id="K8H6ob" name="hl"><option value="de">Deutsch&nbsp;(德语)</option><option value="en">English&nbsp;(英语)</option>